contemplation:
To contemplate the just punishment which God sent upon Korah, Dathan, and Abiram (Numbers 16):

1. How these three incited the people against Moses and Aaron, and sought to become their leaders;

2. How the earth opened and swallowed up Korah, Dathan, Abiram, and others with them;

3. How the earth of the flesh swallows up the souls of all those who think in a fleshly way and, thinking thus, rebel against the Law of God.


HOMILY
